description: Lists the versions of an agent and information about each version.

parameters.name: agentId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the agent.

nested_items.name: agentVersionSummaries
nested_items.description: A list of objects, each of which contains information about a version of the agent.

nested_items.name: agentName
nested_items.description: The name of the agent to which the version belongs.

nested_items.name: agentStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the agent to which the version belongs.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time at which the version was created.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the version of the agent.

nested_items.name: guardrailConfiguration
nested_items.description: Details about the guardrail associated with the agent.

nested_items.name: guardrailIdentifier
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the guardrail.

nested_items.name: updatedAt
nested_items.description: The time at which the version was last updated.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If the total number of results is greater than the maxResults value provided in the request, use this token when making another request in the nextToken field to return the next batch of results.
